{"tid":1846700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果醫護全部集體辭職, 就可以最快達成封關呢個效果","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:05:54.000Z","uid":81154,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f68db8e53eca217db1a1859f0faba8dce06ec0e","tid":1846700,"uid":81154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"成班大陸人知道唔洗錢就可以睇醫生, 一定擁晒落來香港.<br />\n<br />\n到時香港個醫療體係一定崩潰, 咁樣對本身醫院入面既病人, 對醫護來講係人道咩? 係道德咩?<br />\n<br />\n香港班官淨係識刷中共鞋, 幾時有位一個, 係一個香港人諗過呀?<br />\n<br />\n醫護人員你地都知道香港呢個醫療體系係唔可以承受呢次疫症, 點解唔齊心就一齊辭職去迫呢個港<br />\n<br />\n共政府讓步?"},{"pid":"c25d1b947bef08f8922528f1a1e9f14a2688e4d9","tid":1846700,"uid":117235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OX34y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OX34y3.jpg&h=d930b64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WNPfFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WNPfFJ.jpg&h=033f6cbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42ea7a122aed84b35964d5b98301be6e9f831058","tid":1846700,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"其實今次可以直情話係整個世紀香港人罷唔罷到工嘅試金石<br />\n如果今次大家面對疫症+民主困局+無能政府 都罷唔到工嘅<br />\n咁就真係代表永遠香港都罷唔到工㗎啦<br />\n咁場運動真係等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf2845a1dcf1c2e9d6562b76fa3226e5bec0035","tid":1846700,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn